Make map
start end direction
1 2 E
2 3 E
3 4 E
4 5 E
6 7 S
7 3 S
3 8 S
8 9 S

variable defined: HEAR=You hear wind.

scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern @cavern
enter command rest
reject message @msg was printed
enter command @direction
ensure message @msg was printed


script
put pit in cavern 3
message You hear wind. should print when player moves west from cavern 5
Scenario
scenario message msg ShouldPrintWhenPlayerMoves direction FromCavern cavern
put player in cavern 5
enter command rest
reject message You hear wind. was printed
enter command west
ensure message You hear wind. was printed
message You hear wind. should print when player moves east from cavern 1

ensure message You hear wind. was printed
